          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Why Rate Card Communication Requires a Process"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A rate card update changes costs for every team simultaneously. Without a structured communication process, teams discover cost increases on their monthly invoice \u2014 after the budget has already been exceeded. A good process runs impact analysis before the change, notifies affected teams with enough lead time to adjust, and confirms adoption after the cutover."
          }
        ]
      },
