                    ],
                    "text": "Team claims they were not notified"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Show the notification send log with timestamps. If notification failed, apply the old rate retroactively for the gap period."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Team disagrees with impact estimate"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Re-run the impact calculation with their actual usage data and walk through the methodology. If the estimate was wrong, adjust the announcement."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Team cannot absorb the increase in-cycle"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Direct them to the budget exception process (overage approval). The rate card change itself cannot be reversed for one team."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
